International partnerships expand
```

APPENDIX I: METRICS FOR SUCCESS

Technical Metrics:

1. Separation efficiency: >20% (Phase 2), >40% (commercial)
2. Energy consumption: <0.2 kWh/kg (Phase 2), <0.1 kWh/kg (commercial)
3. Reliability: MTBF >10,000 hours (commercial)
4. Autonomy: >95% operations without human intervention

Commercial Metrics:

1. Time to market: First flight 2028, commercial ops 2031
2. Market penetration: 15% of lunar extraction market by 2035
